  "description_snippet": "**VULNERABILITY DETAILS**   \nXML files can contain HTML and thus run javascript if they are delivered as content-type: text/xml. A way to safely deliver user supplied files as raw data is to set the content-type to text/plain instead. This will make all desktop browsers render the XML data as plain"
